name: BENRO A160FBR0 Portable Ball Head Camera Tripod - Black
description:
Benro A160FBR0 Ball Head Tripod
An economic proposal for serious amateurs who start their work with photography. Although it is economical, it provides unique user features such as a ball head, a maximum height of 1.60 m capable of lifting 2 kg while weighing just 1kg so you can carry it comfortably.
From handy tabletop tripods to advanced carbon fiber tripod kits, Benro offers the stability and versatility you need to take your photography to the next level.
We started as a cooperative tripod manufacturer and then began developing and marketing our own brand, Benro in 2002. We continuously invested in advanced tooling and precision machining in concert with a highly trained design/engineering team. We spared nothing in developing and refining the Benro product line. As a result of our commitment to quality and performance, Benro has become one of the most recognized and best selling brands in China as well as a significant global brand known to photographers and filmmakers of every level around the world.

name: Bronx Colors Angel Dust - AD01
description:
THE ANGELS ARE BACK – IN SEDUCTIVE VARIETIES!
No matter what you are wearing or eye color you have this great combination of beautiful eyeshadows ensures you a great look. All these eyeshadows are presented in a lovely tin case and include an applicator.
